Ranger Help for: swiftstrike
=============================

SYNTAX:      swiftstrike <target>
USAGE:       Any terrain
SLOT COST:   13
BASE SP:     90
SKILL TYPE:  attack
REQUIRES:    improvise

SUMMARY:
Swiftstrike drives a Ranger into a focused melee cadence against a single
target. The Ranger must be wielding a slashing weapon. While the rhythm
holds, each slash builds momentum. Every third step in the cadence breaks
open into a violent burst of extra cuts, with stronger payoff when the
Ranger is fighting a favored enemy, moving through favored terrain, or
attacking from a circling flank.

This is a pressure skill, not a single heavy strike. It rewards staying on
one target, reading its movement, and layering other Ranger melee tools on
top of the tempo. Rangers who can circle behind a foe or bring swiftstrike
to bear on a hated enemy will feel the burst become much deadlier.
